<HEAD>Iraqi Feint Led to Major Victory on Faw Peninsula, U.S. Observers
Say</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Gulf Rdp Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By NORMAN BLACK</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>AP Military Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
