<HEAD>Superpowers Dogged by `Serious Differences' Over Regional Wars</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Summit Rdp Bjt</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By ALISON SMALE</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
