 <PERSON> Beam </PERSON> said <ORGANIZATION> AEP </ORGANIZATION> would be `` very much in favor'' of <PERSON> Berry </PERSON>'s strategy if regulators `` could relieve the electric utility industry of its obligation to serve'' all who want to be customers
