nt <PERSON> Phil </PERSON> <PERSON> Bakes </PERSON> last year said the company needed to cut labor costs by some 30 percent overall. Pilots' spokesman <PERSON> Ron </PERSON> <PERSON> Cole </PERSON> said his union, whose contract can be amended on July 1, wo n't be offering major concessions.
